##Shopping cart program
item=input("Enter the item you wanted to buy: ")
price=int(input("Enter the price: "))
quantity=int(input("Enter the quantity: "))
total=price*quantity
print(f"You have bought  {quantity}*{item}")
print(f"Total payable amount {total}")

o/p:
Enter the item you wanted to buy: Pizza
Enter the price: 235
Enter the quantity: 3
You have bought  3*Pizza
Total payable amount 705

